Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:14.97,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:15.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:18.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:23.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:26.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:30.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:34.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:40.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:45.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:48.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:54.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:59.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:03.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:11.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:15.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:18.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:24.92,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,200.389)}Underground Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:24.92,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs205\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(567.167,680.389)}Mogurang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You are blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for sight, I will\Ngive you retractable eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.93,0:01:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that will give you 360-degree\Nvision even while underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These electro-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Mogurang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:01:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mission is to use all\Nthe power at your disposal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to destroy the Kamen Rider\Nand see our plan through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You damned monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment was a roaring success.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My big brother Yutaka\Nis a real good mechanic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He could even help Mr. Ichimonji win\Nthis year's Motocross championships!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me, Big Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask him, too, Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Chairman!\NWon't you let him try?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, don't just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hired, Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Mr. Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That chairman of ours is one swell guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually meant to hire\Nyou from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've talked with Hayato about you two also.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's just one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it true that until six months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you were aiming to be the\Nmotocross champion yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just because you took\Na few spills during races,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you're suddenly afraid\Nto get back on your bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Next year, you race in Ichimonji's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that sound nice, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You look a little flustered... what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I just received a report that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,a man was kidnapped by something\Nhalfway between human and animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Shocker again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:06.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's latest cyborg, Mogurang, could\Nburrow freely through the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:10.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He would pop up, kidnap someone, and\Nreturn them to Shocker's secret base,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:15.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,where they would receive surgery that\Nwould turn them into mole people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Our current goal is to destroy\Nthe Japanese economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally,\Nour primary focus is Tokyo Harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first target will\Nbe the oil refineries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll dump mass quantities of oil\Nfrom their tanks into Tokyo Bay
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and then set the sea aflame!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have left the execution of\Nthis plan to the mole people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Their intelligence has been\Nreduced through surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so that they dig our tunnels day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes forty kidnappings so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like Shocker's\Ndoing something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa, take a break once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The championship is two days away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can finish it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just want to be as careful as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother gets to be a mechanic for\Na motocross bike, just like he wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Do your best, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato is sure to win this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's cheer him on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogurang, how is the plan proceeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir. We're currently here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. At your current pace, we should\Nfinish up tomorrow, as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogurang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your slaves are starting to\Nwork themselves to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and fetch some new ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there, Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A mole monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rider Kick won't work on\Nan underground opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll need to figure out a new move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we know we're\Ndealing with a mole monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we need to be as careful as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogurang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After our current plan succeeds,\NI'll return your human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the restoration fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But your work isn't finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and kidnap Yutaka Aikawa, who's\Ncurrently staying with Tachibana Tobei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to say it, but we might not be able\Nto take part in this year's championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not, Mr. Ichimonji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm extremely sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't apologize enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a liar, Mr. Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a promise to my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato has other things in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hate it so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Yutaka Aikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro! Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call Mr. Ichimonji! Just hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Some weird monster got my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,By the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:42.76,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn on the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's finally entered\Nthe hypnotic state.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yutaka Aikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mission is to kill\NFBI scum Taki Kazuya
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,at the motocross championships\Ntwo days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I will kill Taki Kazuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, failure means death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker must have gotten Hayato, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,While he was trying to save Yutaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they got Yutaka, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't transform while\NI'm tied up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Zol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just woken up and already\Ntrying to escape, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally reached\Nthe end of your rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you take the\Npeople you kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned them into moles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Turned them into moles?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're about to die,\NI might as well tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to drain all the oil from the\NKawasaki/Yokohama oil refinery into Tokyo Bay,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,then set it on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's absurd...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is impossible for Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, the mole-people will arrive\Nbeneath the oil tanks carrying bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When I activate them by the remote control,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it will open holes beneath the tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The oil that flows out will spread,\Nburning, through Tokyo Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Do you like my plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've released that Yutaka boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've released him? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've given him a mission of our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the kind of\Ntrick you would pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Say whatever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We've programmed Yutaka to kill Taki at\Nthe motocross championships tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Taki, rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I foiled Shocker's plot and rescued Aikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's something I need\Nto wrap up before I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can ask a favor, please take my place\Nin the motocross championships. Hayato."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Leave it to me, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it your best shot, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go tune up the bike, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Taki will die...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When I press this button...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it will explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the cyborgs arrived under the tanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Colonel Zol, please\Nblow up the workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll press the detonation\Nswitch in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch remote control over to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparations for the\Ndetonation are in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll blow up our secret base,\Nand Ichimonji Hayato with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This would be a good time\Nto say your prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can cut through these chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Imbibing this will turn them\Nback into normal humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And this will prevent the explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How many left?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogurang, the oil refinery\Ndetonation plan has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider will be heading\Nfor the motocross track.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to fight him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:48.45,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord4\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&}All-Japan Motocross Championships
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki's looking good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll win for sure at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Yutaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Taki's bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:19:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Yutaka working for Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been hypnotized.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That hit I gave him should\Nreturn him to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not Yutaka's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The fault lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... you've foiled\NShocker's plans yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But for the last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has the advantage, here on the soil...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to lure him somewhere\Nmore favorable to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... you unkillable monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Despicable Rider.\NYou won't leave here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... I'll lure him over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.28,0:22:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll knock him into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mogurang?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.77,0:22:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.49,0:22:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to try to kill you, Mr. Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:23:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.22,0:23:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Shocker was just using you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.63,0:23:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time for crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.29,0:23:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a promise to ride in\Nthe race next year yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.33,0:23:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We'll totally win next year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Root for him, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:30.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato, the Kamen\NRider, defeated Mogurang
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:34.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and protected Tokyo from an\Nattack on its oil refineries.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:37.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He renewed his pledge to fight Shocker as\Nhe continued to wish for peace in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:40.77,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:43.05,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:45.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.36,0:23:47.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the electric monster Kuragedall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:49.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kuragedall appears and disappears at will,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.83,0:23:53.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,kidnapping villagers and turning\Nthem into electro-people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:24:01.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen Rider\N in "The Electric Monster Kuragedall!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:24:01.14,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fscy90\fs131\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(547.167,720.389)}The Electric Monster Kuragedall!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.34,0:24:11.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:13.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:15.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.72,0:24:18.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.27,0:24:21.14,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.14,0:24:23.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:24.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.81,0:24:26.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.61,0:24:28.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.70,0:24:34.37,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.37,0:24:37.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.95,0:24:41.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.04,0:24:45.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Underground Monster Mogurang